<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .contract-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background: white;
        }
        .contract-table th {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .contract-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .contract-table tr:hover {
            background: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .badge-urgent {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .badge-warning {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        .badge-info {
            background: #dbeafe;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⚠️ Notification de Contrats Expirants</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Bonjour,</p>
        
        <p>Nous vous informons que <strong>{{ contracts|length }} contrat(s)</strong> de sponsoring {{ contracts|length > 1 ? 'expirent' : 'expire' }} dans les <strong>{{ days }} prochains jours</strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>⚠️ Action requise :</strong> Veuillez prendre les mesures nécessaires pour renouveler ou gérer ces contrats avant leur expiration.
        </div>
        
        <h2>Détails des contrats expirants :</h2>
        
        <table class="contract-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Numéro</th>
                    <th>Sponsor</th>
                    <th>Email</th>
                    <th>Date d'expiration</th>
                    <th>Jours restants</th>
                    <th>Niveau</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for contract in contracts %}
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{ contract.contractNumber }}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{ contract.sponsor ? contract.sponsor.name : 'N/A' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ contract.sponsor ? contract.sponsor.email : 'N/A' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ contract.expiresAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</td>
                    <td>
                        {% set daysLeft = contract.daysUntilExpiration %}
                        {% if daysLeft <= 7 %}
                            <span class="badge badge-urgent">{{ daysLeft }} jour(s)</span>
                        {% elseif daysLeft <= 15 %}
                            <span class="badge badge-warning">{{ daysLeft }} jour(s)</span>
                        {% else %}
                            <span class="badge badge-info">{{ daysLeft }} jour(s)</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td>{{ contract.level ? contract.level.value : 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Période de notification :</strong> {{ periodStart|date('d/m/Y') }} - {{ periodEnd|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
        
        <p>Cordialement,<br>Système de Gestion des Sponsors</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Cet email a été généré automatiquement. Veuillez ne pas y répondre.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

